by SpacePossum at 2017-01-27T05:49:07Z

What is left here is to decide to add more configuration options for setting which kind of comparisons should be fixed. Based on previous discussions it seems some people would like to target no-vars like `(array(2))` and `self::MY_CONST` while other don't. Like to get some feedback so this fixer can finished :)

